\id 3JN - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG 3 John 12/2/91 Macnaughtan 
\h 3 DIONI 
\toc1 Dionimaęž‰ tepo peao tapaeyeke wapee 
\toc2 3 Dioni 
\toc3 3 Dioni 
\mt1 Dionimaęž‰ tepo peao tapaeyeke wapee  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 IĚ±taęž‰ you halimaęž‰ mo yaka pukimaęž‰ homolo yankeke Kaiasi paęž‰taęž‰ do tameiyaęž‰ tapaasome.   
\p
\v 2 Yaka yankekeo. IĚ±maęž‰ neke yeni peaaso ekitaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ pitele haumanu paeyao epeke tupaęž‰ puelenaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰ yeni maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hake honkopu hao halenaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Hande nakaęž‰ temoko epeke tupaęž‰ halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ hone witolo loaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Mo mandane Ketiso kamemanu opolo aęž‰pa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo otaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ ki hone na wiki pa putia pulieki aęž‰pa lemeke handaa IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homoaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Nakaęž‰ hoto paeyao mo hande otaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hao hale tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Yaka weki wandikitaęž‰ mo otaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halemeeki opitoloeki homekemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ wopu peaasaęž‰me.   
\s1 Kaiasi yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 5 Yaka yankekeo. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ Ketiso tapake paęž‰taęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homeke tambaęž‰ mu hale tupaęž‰ kone mo neke na handeke Ketiso tapake paęž‰taęž‰ make homeke tupaęž‰ kone tambaęž‰ mu haleme.  
\v 6 Koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ do haleme siosi tapake paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeleeki aęž‰pa la halememe. Koto wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ potaęž‰ pulimi ale paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaalo peleme tambaęž‰ meaęž‰peke laa honke alome.  
\v 7 Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hone na tulaaleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kiaaso hataęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaaluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone kini pimime.  
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ niki Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ dupiki wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ mumanaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke ikaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ e pokelemeeki telipumanaęž‰ loaęž‰me.   
\s1 Daeodaęž‰taęž‰pisi pitaęž‰ Dimiditiasi yaapo  
\p
\v 9 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ dokaęž‰tiki tameiyaęž‰ siki tapaowaęž‰pate mo siosinaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali haluekee hone wieke hali Daeodaęž‰taęž‰pisimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na opu halaęž‰me.  
\v 10 IĚ± epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu paeyao lo kelalueke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ keke pi laęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make mo ipikaęž‰ yayapiki pimanu lo halaęž‰eki paeyao tonkaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me. Do hande haumanu homeke anaęž‰e hone na u halaęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kimisu ipilimi Ketiso kamemanu epemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ na handaęž‰ milieke. Kutupa handaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ taapo haleme wandaęž‰hali make saęž‰saęž‰ pea mo yeni da minaęž‰paęž‰lao hama penaęž‰ lenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ taapo halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 11 Yaka yankekeo. Mo hokeeki na mokaęž‰la handeketaęž‰ mo epekeeki homeke mokaęž‰la handaęž‰peke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ epekeeki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ ekie. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ hokeeki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ na handeke some halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ Dimiditiasitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lo halememe. Ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ pimaęž‰ kone aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lo halaęž‰me. Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make homeke pi kone lo halomaęž‰me. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ alomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ekie hone wilime.   
\s1 Paeyaaso pimanu  
\p
\v 13 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰peke pitaęž‰ wopu ulaęž‰pate mo wape laasaęž‰ tanumaęž‰ laapeketaęž‰ IĚ± ki paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 14 Yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ neke koto kone handolo ipulu hataęž‰ pimanu lopanaęž‰e.   
\p
\v 15 Puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki neke paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰e. Nakaęž‰ yankeke tonu paeyaomaęž‰ aęž‰taloe lo tapaasememe. Nikaęž‰ yankeke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰talo lawaapekee.   